<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PROJECT AMDIS // DECLASSIFIED</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=VT323&display=swap');

        :root {
            --bg-color: #050505;
            --text-color: #00ff41;
            --red-alert: #ff003c;
            --redacted-bg: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* CRT Scanline Effect */
        body::after {
            content: " ";
            display: block;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 50%), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.06), rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.02), rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.06));
            z-index: 2;
            background-size: 100% 2px, 3px 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 10;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed var(--text-color);
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .warning {
            color: var(--red-alert);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            animation: blink 2s infinite;
        }

        .lore-box {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Redacted Text Effect */
        .redacted {
            background-color: var(--text-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            padding: 0 4px;
            user-select: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .revealed .redacted {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff;
        }

        /* The Big Red Button */
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }

        #discombobulate-btn {
            background-color: var(--red-alert);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
            font-size: 3rem;
            padding: 1rem 3rem;
            border: 4px solid #8b0000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 0 #8b0000, 0 15px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.1s;
        }

        #discombobulate-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 0px 0 #8b0000, 0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        /* Contract Address Reveal */
        .ca-box {
            display: none;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s forwards;
        }

        .ca-text {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .social-links a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--text-color);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            background: var(--text-color);
            color: var(--bg-color);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Glitch Effect applied to body during button press */
        .glitching {
            animation: glitch-anim 0.3s cubic-bezier(.25, .46, .45, .94) both infinite;
            filter: hue-rotate(90deg) invert(10%);
        }

        @keyframes glitch-anim {
            0% { transform: translate(0) }
            20% { transform: translate(-5px, 5px) }
            40% { transform: translate(-5px, -5px) }
            60% { transform: translate(5px, 5px) }
            80% { transform: translate(5px, -5px) }
            100% { transform: translate(0) }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container" id="main-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="warning">TOP SECRET // EYES ONLY</h1>
            <h2>OPERATION: EPIC FURY // PROJECT $AMDIS</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="lore-box">
            <p>> SYSTEM INITIALIZED...</p>
            <p>> INCOMING TRANSMISSION...</p>
            <br>
            <p>They thought they were ready. They had the rockets. They had the buttons.</p>
            <p>Then we activated <span class="redacted">THE DISCOMBOBULATOR</span>.</p>
            <p>"We came in, they pressed buttons and <span class="redacted">NOTHING WORKED</span>."</p>
            <br>
            <p>The weapon isn't just hardware. It is now on-chain. When the market panics, when the bears try to drop red candles, the system jams their signals.</p>
            <p>> STATUS: <span style="color: var(--red-alert);">AWAITING MANUAL OVERRIDE</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-container" id="action-area">
            <audio id="trump-audio" src="YOUR_AUDIO_LINK_HERE.mp3" preload="auto"></audio>
            
            <button id="discombobulate-btn">DECLASSIFY</button>
        </div>

        <div class="ca-box" id="ca-reveal">
            <h2>🚨 WEAPON DEPLOYED 🚨</h2>
            <p>OFFICIAL CONTRACT ADDRESS:</p>
            <div class="ca-text" id="ca-string">D8KqdmF91kV8AA13kpZrdYjPQXNUt5uCDTkAgqKopump</div>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://x.com/Operationamdis" target="_blank">X (TWITTER)</a>
                <a href="https://t.me/americandiscumbobulator" target="_blank">TELEGRAM</a>
                <a href="https://pump.fun/D8KqdmF91kV8AA13kpZrdYjPQXNUt5uCDTkAgqKopump" target="_blank">PUMP.FUN</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const btn = document.getElementById('discombobulate-btn');
        const container = document.getElementById('main-container');
        const caBox = document.getElementById('ca-reveal');
        const actionArea = document.getElementById('action-area');
        const audio = document.getElementById('trump-audio');

        btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            // 1. Play the audio
            // Note: If you don't have an audio file yet, remove or comment out the line below so it doesn't error.
            // audio.play().catch(e => console.log("Audio play failed, user interaction needed or bad link."));
            
            // 2. Trigger visual glitch
            document.body.classList.add('glitching');
            btn.innerText = "JAMMING SIGNAL...";
            
            // 3. After 1.5 seconds, reveal the CA and stop glitching
            setTimeout(() => {
                document.body.classList.remove('glitching');
                container.classList.add('revealed'); // Un-redacts text
                actionArea.style.display = 'none'; // Hides button
                caBox.style.display = 'block'; // Shows CA
            }, 1500);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
